+        // For INV-3 (p₀=1e-6, λ=0.9, α=0.001) with p₁=0.01:
+        // KL(0.01 || 1e-6) ≈ 0.01·ln(10000) + 0.99·ln(0.99/0.999999) ≈ 0.0921
